  "intent_precise": "1f96ca.ot2.apiv2: Using reagent_block (plate, slot 5), mag_plate (pcr_plate, slot 4), temporary_plate (plate, slot 1), reservoir (reservoir, slot 2). With thermocycler module, magnetic module. (1) Wait 12 seconds. (2) Pause: message (3) Transfer from source to destination. (4) Wait 1 seconds. (5) Open thermocycler lid. (6) Set temperature to 4\u00b0C. (7) Disengage magnets to release beads. (8) Transfer 7\u00b5L from source A1 to destination A1. (9) Close thermocycler lid. (10) Wait 15 seconds. (11) Run thermocycler profile for 1 cycles. (12) Set temperature to 4\u00b0C. (13) Open thermocycler lid. (14) Transfer 2\u00b5L from source A1 to destination A1. (15) Close thermocycler lid. (16) Operate thermocycler. (17) Run thermocycler profile for 1 cycles. (18) Set temperature to 4\u00b0C. (19) Open thermocycler lid. (20) Transfer 10\u00b5L from source A1 to destination A1. (21) Close thermocycler lid. (22) Set temperature to 20\u00b0C. (23) Incubate for 1.0 hours. (24) Transfer 18\u00b5L from source A1 to destination A1. (25) Incubate for 15 minutes. (26) Engage magnets for bead separation. (27) Pause for incubation. (28) Transfer 40\u00b5L from source A1 to destination A1. (29) Wait 30 seconds. (30) Pause for incubation. (31) Disengage magnets to release beads. (32) Transfer 10\u00b5L from source A1 to destination A1. (33) Incubate for 20 minutes. (34) Engage magnets for bead separation. (35) Pause for incubation. (36) Open thermocycler lid. (37) Transfer 10\u00b5L from source A1 to destination A1. (38) Distribute 1\u00b5L from source A1 to destination wells A1, A1, A1. (39) Close thermocycler lid. (40) Operate thermocycler. (41) Run thermocycler profile for reps cycles. (42) Set temperature to 4\u00b0C. (43) Open thermocycler lid.",
  "intent_concise": "Perform distribute to A1, A1, A1, magnetic bead separation, temperature control (4\u00b0C, 20\u00b0C), thermocycling. (volumes 1\u00b5L-100\u00b5L, ~97 min total)",
  "intent": "Alright, let's set up the OT-2 with the reagent block in slot 5, mag plate in slot 4, temporary plate in slot 1, and reservoir in slot 2, making sure both the thermocycler and magnetic modules are ready to go. Start by waiting 12 seconds, then pause for confirmation before doing your initial transfers - you'll be moving through a series of additions to well A1: first 7\u00b5L, then 2\u00b5L, then 10\u00b5L, with thermocycler cycles at 4\u00b0C between each addition. The protocol then moves into incubation phases at 20\u00b0C for 1 hour, followed by bead separations with magnet engagement/disengagement, including an 18\u00b5L addition, 15-minute incubation, then a 40\u00b5L transfer with 30-second wait, and finally a 10\u00b5L addition with 20-minute incubation. Finish up by transferring a final 10\u00b5L to A1, distribute 1\u00b5L to three A1 wells, run your final thermocycler profile for the specified number of cycles, cool to 4\u00b0C, and open the lid.",
